descriptionNullable:
This report utilizes the COVID-19 Response Reporting data of Mass.gov.  The dataset includes Daily and cumulative reports on Massachusetts COVID-19 cases, testing, and hospitalizations. It contains information from nursing homes, city/town cases, and state facilities. For each category, the collection contains 31 separate tables. 

In this dataset, infections are categorized according to age, gender, ethnicity, race, and county. For each group, the frequency of the collection varies, such as daily, weekly, and biweekly. Following are the tables which we are going to use for our project along with their description. 

Created By: Husain Rangwala;  Dhara Kalola;  Jianwei Li
